cabal-lua-intro-1 =
    A cyborg squad and a Hacker Drone will aid you in this mission.
    We have to use a small squad to hide our purpose at the beginning.
cabal-lua-intro-2 =
    Use our Hacker Drone to hack this Civilian Array for local intelligence.
    Hacker Drone is the key to this mission, protect it.
tip-lua-usage-hacker =
    How to use Hacker Drone:
    1.Target hackable (such as Civilian Array) to send its Quadrotor to hack (Range: 20 cells).
    2.Target capturable building to capture the building by itself.
    3.Force fire at location to send its Quadrotor to recon (Range: 20 cells). Can detect cloaked.

cabal-lua-mcv-located = M.C.V. located, we find our Defender mech and a Nod's mech prototype. We can restart our Defender mech once the M.C.V. is captured.
warning-lua-mcv-located = Successfully capture the MCV will start the direct conflict between Nod! Be prepared!
tip-lua-mcv-located = Explore the map more before recapture the MCV. You may need more resources from civilian, or find a place to relocate this MCV.
warning-lua-mcv-being-captured = Nod has noticed our attempt and tries to restart the MCV!

cabal-lua-mcv-captured-success-1 = Our Defender mech is online. Beware, it cannot be rebuilt in this mission, use it wisely.
cabal-lua-mcv-captured-success-2 = Thanks to your efforts on hacking arrays, Nod's mech prototype is now our toy.
cabal-lua-mcv-captured-success-reinforce-1 = Our heavy support is on the way.
cabal-lua-mcv-captured-success-reinforce-2 = More cyborgs are on the way to aid you.

warning-lua-mcv-captured-success-1 = Nod has been awared of the activation of our MCV and our hacking to Civilian Arrays, in the intercepted message.
warning-lua-mcv-captured-success-2 =
    Be prepared for a face to face combat.
    Nod plans to destroy all Civilian Arrays to prevent further cyber attack.

cabal-lua-mcv-captured-failed-1 = The M.C.V. is lost again, but it is not over.
cabal-lua-mcv-captured-failed-2 = Nod believes our failure is inevitable and no longer pay attention to us, in the intercepted message.
cabal-lua-mcv-captured-failed-3 = It is an oppotunity, let us hack remaining Civilian Arrays and try a cyber attack to cripple their main base.

warning-lua-nod-aware-attack = Nod has been awared of our attack on their main base, be prepared for a face to face combat.
cabal-lua-hack-one-array-1 = We can now intercept some of their communication and 3 other Civilian Arrays can be located.
cabal-lua-hack-one-array-2 = It is confirmed that the unknow signal is from an alien origin. Use our cyborg squad to find it.
cabal-lua-hack-one-array-3 =
    There are two enemies: Nod and their local Armed Civilians.
    The Armed Civilians has a rather old armory, should be easier to deal with.

cabal-lua-hack-two-array = Hacker Drone can now disable the control system of enemy defence and vehicle by hacking.
tip-lua-hack-two-array = Hacker Drone can now use its Quadrotor to disable enemy's defence and vehicle!

cabal-lua-hack-three-array-1 = With more accessibility, we get some information of Nod's research of our MCV. Nod steals our technology for their 'Avatar' project.
cabal-lua-hack-three-array-2 = We have revealed all the 'Avatar' project related by hacking. We will launch a cyber attack when the final Civilian Array is hacked
warning-lua-hack-three-array = Successfully hack into the final Civilian Array will start the direct conflict between Nod! Be prepared!


cabal-lua-hack-four-array-1 =
    Our cyber attack will
    1.Make 'Avatar' project lose control.
    2.Sabotage Nod's power system for a short period.
cabal-lua-hack-four-array-2 = Take the chance to destroy Nod's base and find that alien obejct.
warning-lua-hack-four-array-1 = Nod has been awared of our hacking and consider us a major threat, in the intercepted message.
warning-lua-hack-four-array-2 =
    Be prepared for a face to face combat.
    Nod are likely to restart our lost MCV to against us.

cabal-lua-find-alien = It seems this alien structure is the source of the unkown signals, capture it.

cabal-lua-find-mercenary-1 = Interesting, we also intercepted an advertisement from a Mutant Mercenaries.
cabal-lua-find-mercenary-2 = Their position is located, they can be useful to us.

warlord-lua-intro-1 = Well well well, bros and gals, look what do we have here! I never expect those cyborgs can walk this far.
warlord-lua-intro-2 = Cool it, boys. Anyway, cyborgs, we are businessmen, and I am sure CABAL taught you how to deal.
warlord-lua-intro-3 = If you want, we can help you, for a price, in FULL PAYMENT and no refund.
warlord-lua-intro-4 = And always remember, don't mess up with us, kiddo.
warlord-lua-mad = Enough! KILL EVERYTHING THAT IS NOT MUTANT!

