soldier-lua-intro-2 = Yeah, I just saw Brotherhood Of Nerds got that MCV again, the timming was perfect LOL.
soldier-lua-intro-3 = Feh, glad that they cannot do s**t here. Brotherhood Of Nerds still has their MCV.
soldier-lua-intro-4 = (thumbs safety catch) Feh, I guess they can walk no further if their legs are broken.

